metadata.name: Christmas tree
metadata.description:
This is 1 NFT in a collection of 5 short videos that have been released as a single, unique edition.

Video: 2000 x 2000 px

The Christmas tree is a traditional attribute of Christmas celebrations in many countries around the world.

The Christmas tree is decorated with garlands, Christmas toys, candles or bulbs.

Christmas is a time of magic, it is the most anticipated and definitely the most magical holiday!
